            <thetext>When we generate the skeleton of a new app we need to run &quot;create-application.py  -n appname&quot;, -n beeing a required option for the application name. 

The command should be easier if we just run &quot;create-application.py appname&quot; and use an argument instead of a required option for the appname. This is how generate.py works for all the qooxdoo jobs (i.e. generate.py source) and it makes more sense.</thetext>
